transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Haan abhi to kya keh rahe aap?
Executive: Hello
Customer: Haanji sir bataiye.
Customer: Haan abhi sunai pad raha hai na to aap Google Meet ke liye bol rahe the?
Executive: Haan Google Meet ke liye sir bol rahi thi, bataiye.
Customer: Haan wohi bol raha hu mai 10 minute baad aapko call karke Google Meet join kar raha hu, thik hai?
Executive: Achha 10 minute baad aap join karenge?
Customer: Ji ji ji.
Executive: Thik hai sir thik hai mai na aapko
Executive: Sir ye jo aapki mail id hai mai ek baar confirm kar leti hu registered mail id jo aapki.
Executive: Uh sir ye jo hai aapki
Executive: Ek baar confirm karungi sir aapki mail id?
Customer: Hmm.
Customer: S.t.o.e.n.g.g@gmail.com
Executive: S.t.l.b@gmail.com
Customer: S.t.o.e.n.g.g@gmail.com
Executive: Thik hai. Sir ek S.t.o jo aapka registered mail hai na jo S.t.o kar karke hai last p.l.g.g hai and @gmail.com hai ye, thik hai sir? Hmm.
Executive: To mai ispe na aapka aapko link share kar deti hu, ek minute. Aapka basically abhi timing rahegi sir 11:30 ki kar rahi hu, thik hai sir?
Customer: 11:30, haanji haanji.
Executive: Hello? Haanji haanji.
Executive: Thik hai sir 11:30 ka mai kar deti hu sir.
Customer: Haan haan. Thank you sir, thank you.
Executive: Thank you, thank you.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer wants to join Google Meet.

- Executive needs to confirm customer's email ID.



Resolution:

- Executive confirmed the customer's email ID.

- Executive will share the Google Meet link.

- Google Meet scheduled for 11:30.



Next Steps: 

None

Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

- google meet, email id, confirmation
